---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Logo from '../components/Logo.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Delete Your Account"
  description="Learn how to request deletion of your Subscriptin account and associated data."
>
  <div class="min-h-screen" style="width: 100%;">
    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="surface elevation-1 sticky top-0 z-10" style="width: 100%;">
      <div style="max-width: 80rem; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1.5rem;">
        <a href="/" class="hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity" style="display: flex; justify-content: center;">
          <Logo size="small" />
        </a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Delete Account Content -->
    <main style="width: 100%;">
      <div style="max-width: 80rem; margin: 0 auto; padding: 5rem 1.5rem 8rem 1.5rem;">
        <!-- Surface container for better readability -->
        <article class="surface elevation-1 rounded-3xl delete-content" style="padding: 4rem;">
          <h1>Delete Your Subscriptin Account</h1>

          <p class="intro-text">
            We understand that you may want to delete your Subscriptin account. This page explains how to request account deletion and what happens to your data.
          </p>

          <h2>How to Request Account Deletion</h2>

          <p>To request deletion of your Subscriptin account and associated data, please follow these steps:</p>

          <ol>
            <li>Send an email to <a href="mailto:support@subscriptin.com">support@subscriptin.com</a> from the email address associated with your account</li>
            <li>Include "Account Deletion Request" in the subject line</li>
            <li>In the email body, confirm that you want to permanently delete your account and all associated data</li>
            <li>You will receive a confirmation email within 2 business days acknowledging your request</li>
            <li>Your account and data will be deleted within 30 days of your request</li>
          </ol>

          <div class="important-notice">
            <h3>⚠️ Important</h3>
            <p>Account deletion is permanent and cannot be undone. Please make sure you want to proceed before submitting your request.</p>
          </div>

          <h2>What Data Gets Deleted</h2>

          <p>When you request account deletion, the following data will be permanently removed from our systems:</p>

          <ul>
            <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Your email address, username, and profile settings</li>
            <li><strong>Subscription Data:</strong> All subscription entries you've created, including names, costs, renewal dates, and notes</li>
            <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Your app usage patterns, preferences, and settings</li>
            <li><strong>Analytics Data:</strong> Any insights, reports, or analytics generated from your subscription data</li>
            <li><strong>Authentication Data:</strong> Login credentials and authentication tokens</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>Data Retention Period</h2>

          <p>Most of your data is deleted within 30 days of your deletion request. However, some information may be retained for the following periods:</p>

          <ul>
            <li><strong>Transaction Records:</strong> Financial transaction records may be retained for up to 7 years to comply with legal and tax requirements</li>
            <li><strong>Anonymized Analytics:</strong> Aggregated, anonymized usage statistics that cannot identify you personally may be retained indefinitely for product improvement</li>
            <li><strong>Legal Compliance:</strong> Any data required to be retained by law will be kept for the minimum required period</li>
            <li><strong>Backup Systems:</strong> Data in backup systems will be deleted within 90 days as backups are cycled</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>What Happens After Deletion</h2>

          <p>Once your account is deleted:</p>

          <ul>
            <li>You will no longer be able to log in to Subscriptin</li>
            <li>All your subscription tracking data will be permanently removed</li>
            <li>You will not receive any further notifications or emails from us (except a final deletion confirmation)</li>
            <li>Your email address can be used to create a new account in the future if desired</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>Alternative: Temporary Account Deactivation</h2>

          <p>If you're not sure about permanently deleting your account, you can request temporary deactivation instead:</p>

          <ul>
            <li>Contact <a href="mailto:support@subscriptin.com">support@subscriptin.com</a> to request account deactivation</li>
            <li>Your account will be deactivated but your data will be preserved for up to 90 days</li>
            <li>You can reactivate your account during this period by contacting support</li>
            <li>After 90 days of deactivation, your account may be permanently deleted</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>Questions or Concerns?</h2>

          <p>If you have any questions about the account deletion process or data retention, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@subscriptin.com">support@subscriptin.com</a>. We're here to help.</p>

          <p>For more information about how we handle your data, please see our <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>

        </article>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <footer class="border-t border-[var(--color-outline-variant)] dark:border-[var(--color-outline-variant-dark)] text-center" style="margin-top: 8rem; padding-top: 3rem;">
          <p class="body-large text-[var(--color-on-surface-variant)] dark:text-[var(--color-on-surface-variant-dark)] leading-relaxed footer-text">
            Need help? Email us at{' '}
            <a
              href="mailto:support@subscriptin.com"
              class="text-[var(--color-primary)] dark:text-[var(--color-primary-dark)] hover:underline font-medium"
            >
              support@subscriptin.com
            </a>
          </p>
          <p class="body-medium text-[var(--color-on-surface-variant)] dark:text-[var(--color-on-surface-variant-dark)]">
            © 2024 Subscriptin. All rights reserved.
          </p>
        </footer>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style is:global>
  /* Page padding */
  .page-padding {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    padding-right: 1.5rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .page-padding {
      padding-left: 2rem;
      padding-right: 2rem;
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .page-padding {
      padding-left: 3rem;
      padding-right: 3rem;
    }
  }

  /* Desktop spacing (default) */
  .header-padding {
    padding-top: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .main-padding {
    padding-top: 5rem;
    padding-bottom: 8rem;
  }

  .article-padding {
    padding: 4rem;
  }

  .footer-spacing {
    margin-top: 8rem;
    padding-top: 3rem;
  }

  .footer-text {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  /* Mobile spacing (640px and below) */
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .header-padding {
      padding-top: 1.5rem;
      padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .main-padding {
      padding-top: 3rem;
      padding-bottom: 4rem;
    }

    .article-padding {
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    .footer-spacing {
      margin-top: 4rem;
      padding-top: 2rem;
    }

    .footer-text {
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
  }

  /* Very small mobile (400px and below) */
  @media (max-width: 400px) {
    .header-padding {
      padding-top: 1rem;
      padding-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .main-padding {
      padding-top: 2rem;
      padding-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .article-padding {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .footer-spacing {
      margin-top: 3rem;
    }
  }

  /* Delete Account Content Styling - Material 3 */
  .delete-content {
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .delete-content h1 {
    font-size: 2.25rem !important;
    line-height: 2.75rem !important;
    font-weight: 400 !important;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem !important;
    margin-top: 0 !important;
    text-align: center !important;
    color: var(--color-primary) !important;
  }

  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    .delete-content h1 {
      color: var(--color-primary-dark) !important;
    }
  }

  .delete-content .intro-text {
    font-size: 1.125rem !important;
    line-height: 1.875rem !important;
    text-align: center !important;
    margin-bottom: 3rem !important;
    color: var(--color-on-surface-variant) !important;
  }

  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    .delete-content .intro-text {
      color: var(--color-on-surface-variant-dark) !important;
    }
  }

  .delete-content h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem !important;
    line-height: 2rem !important;
    font-weight: 400 !important;
    margin-top: 4rem !important;
    margin-bottom: 2rem !important;
    padding-bottom: 1rem !important;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-outline-variant) !important;
    color: var(--color-on-surface) !important;
  }

  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    .delete-content h2 {
      color: var(--color-on-surface-dark) !important;
      border-bottom-color: var(--color-outline-variant-dark) !important;
    }
  }

  .delete-content h2:first-of-type {
    margin-top: 2rem !important;
  }

  .delete-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.125rem !important;
    line-height: 1.5rem !important;
    font-weight: 500 !important;
    margin-top: 0 !important;
    margin-bottom: 1rem !important;
    color: var(--color-primary) !important;
  }

  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    .delete-content h3 {
      color: var(--color-primary-dark) !important;
    }
  }

  .delete-content p {
    font-size: 1rem !important;
    line-height: 1.875rem !important;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem !important;
    margin-top: 0 !important;
    color: var(--color-on-surface-variant) !important;
  }

  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    .delete-content p {
      color: var(--color-on-surface-variant-dark) !important;
    }
  }

  .delete-content strong {
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-on-surface);
  }

  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    .delete-content strong {
      color: var(--color-on-surface-dark);
    }
  }

  .delete-content a {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }

  .delete-content a:hover {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    .delete-content a {
      color: var(--color-primary-dark);
    }
  }

  /* Lists */
  .delete-content ul,
  .delete-content ol {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem !important;
    margin-top: 0.5rem !important;
    padding-left: 1.5rem !important;
    color: var(--color-on-surface-variant) !important;
  }

  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    .delete-content ul,
    .delete-content ol {
      color: var(--color-on-surface-variant-dark) !important;
    }
  }

  .delete-content ul {
    list-style-type: disc !important;
  }

  .delete-content ol {
    list-style-type: decimal !important;
  }

  .delete-content li {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem !important;
    line-height: 1.75rem !important;
    font-size: 1rem !important;
  }

  .delete-content li:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0 !important;
  }

  /* Important Notice Box */
  .delete-content .important-notice {
    background-color: rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.1);
    border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
  }

  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    .delete-content .important-notice {
      background-color: rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.15);
    }
  }

  .delete-content .important-notice h3 {
    margin-top: 0 !important;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem !important;
    color: #f57c00 !important;
  }

  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    .delete-content .important-notice h3 {
      color: #ffa726 !important;
    }
  }

  .delete-content .important-notice p {
    margin-bottom: 0 !important;
  }

  /* Mobile responsiveness */
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .delete-content h1 {
      font-size: 1.875rem !important;
      line-height: 2.25rem !important;
    }

    .delete-content .intro-text {
      font-size: 1rem !important;
      line-height: 1.625rem !important;
    }

    .delete-content h2 {
      font-size: 1.25rem !important;
      line-height: 1.75rem !important;
    }

    .delete-content h3 {
      font-size: 1rem !important;
      line-height: 1.5rem !important;
    }

    .delete-content p {
      font-size: 0.9375rem !important;
      line-height: 1.625rem !important;
    }

    .delete-content li {
      font-size: 0.9375rem !important;
      line-height: 1.625rem !important;
    }

    .delete-content ul,
    .delete-content ol {
      padding-left: 1.25rem !important;
    }

    .delete-content .important-notice {
      padding: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
